Installation

You can install the released version of gpbStat from CRAN with:

install.packages("gpbStat")

Example

Sample example for RCBD analysis


library(gpbStat)

## Load data

data("alphalt")

results1 = ltcalpha(alphalt, replication, block, line, tester, yield)
